{"tid":2357321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：特朗普支持者衝擊國會致4死後　拜登獲確認當選總統","createTime":"2021-01-07T10:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T11:29:15.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a41ef4876a828ebb8fe9901c5d44414200795645","tid":2357321,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國國會確認民主黨的拜登獲得足夠選舉人票，當選新一任總統。</strong>現任特朗普表示，雖然完全不認同選舉結果，但仍會在本月20日有序進行政權交接。<br />\n<br />\n在國會舉行確認大選各州選舉人投票結果程序的會議期間，<strong>特朗普一批支持者闖入國會山莊</strong>，導致會議被逼暫停。示威者與警方爆發激烈衝突，1名女子中槍不治，另外有3人送院後死亡，52人被捕，衝突其後平息，聯席會議重開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569191-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569191-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=0af3a366\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569191-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=30693a2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569191-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4cc92341d0fe520c6ad7f61242e993b82d746f24","tid":2357321,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"不如你教我點寫"},{"pid":"62e72e9a9729feecb6f99ee05dbcc86d06375775","tid":2357321,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a41ef4876a828ebb8fe9901c5d44414200795645","tid":2357321,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國國會確認民主黨的拜登獲得足夠選舉人票，當選新一任總統。</strong>現任特朗普表示，雖然完全不認同選舉結果，但仍會在本月20日有序進行政權交接。<br />\n<br />\n在國會舉行確認大選各州選舉人投票結果程序的會議期間，<strong>特朗普一批支持者闖入國會山莊</strong>，導致會議被逼暫停。示威者與警方爆發激烈衝突，1名女子中